**Addition of digits in the Number even odd



def digitsum(n):
    digit_sum =0
    for digit in str(n):
        digit_sum+=int(digit)
    return digit_sum
        

List_1 = [12, 13, 14, 15, 16, 17, 18]

Even_List = [digitsum(i) for i in List_1 if not i&1]
Odd_List = [digitsum(i) for i in List_1 if i&1]

print("Even List:- ", Even_List)
print("Odd List:- ", Odd_List)

OUTPUT

Even List:-  [3, 5, 7, 9]
Odd List:-  [4, 6, 8]
